{"tid":253190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方日報直擊國泰炒人！員工大袋細袋要走後門離開！","createTime":"2017-05-22T08:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T13:03:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e929ab616334d6b917e972e83a62e400ab02aff","tid":253190,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170522/photo/bkn-20170522112056127-0522_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170522%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170522112056127-0522_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=4cac246d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170522/photo/bkn-20170522112056127-0522_00822_001_02p.jpg?20170522123235\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170522%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170522112056127-0522_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20170522123235&h=d9840223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰城後門有4輛黑色七人車，有司機透露「嚟車人」。(黃雄攝)<br />\n<br />\n因管理不善而從全球最佳航空公司排名榜節節下跌的國泰航空，今日開始派大信封，分階段裁減約600名總部員工，在總部的後門，更見到有手持一袋袋物品的員工，據知他們是協助被裁員工搬走物品。 <br />\n<br />\n雖然工會指公司未有安排車輛接送被裁員工，但東網記者今早在國泰城後門見到有4輛黑色七人車，約10時10分在場等候，有司機更向記者透露「嚟車人」，並是今早才收到公司通知，臨時被召回接載員工。其後有一行五人拿着大包小包從後門步出，並走向停車場方向，但就聲稱是「幫人拎走」。"},{"pid":"d31ad1d2d5f3ba8ac4d9613ed3a432fbd45abf36","tid":253190,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:03:38.000Z","msg":"點解東方要影空姐PAT PAT？<br />\n<br />\n明明無炒空姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170522/photo/bkn-20170522084423757-0522_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170522155921\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170522%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170522084423757-0522_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170522155921&h=7f5fd306&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcb70688d8399e9bb41f8fea97d6fdbca643fb1a","tid":253190,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:04: